OL,3,CPM adviser says police should be able
OL,4,Cto 'disperse' protests around
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FBy ITV News Westminster Producer, Maya
OL,8,FBowles
OL,10,FThe PM's adviser on political violence
OL,11,Fsays the government should look at
OL,12,Fgiving police more powers to
OL,13,F"disperse" protests outside
OL,14,FParliament, MPs offices, and council
OL,15,Fchambers, amid questions about MP's
OL,16,Fsafety.
OL,18,FLord Walney, said "aggressive protests
OL,19,Fare not an expression of liberal
OL,20,Fdemocracy", but a "threat to liberal
OL,21,Fdemocracy".
