OL,7,FThe security adviser will make the
OL,8,Frecommendations in a government-
OL,9,Fcommissioned review into tackling
OL,10,Fpolitical violence which he has been
OL,11,Fwriting for the last three years.
OL,13,FIt comes after the Speaker of the
OL,14,FHouse of Commons said his decision to
OL,15,Fdefy parliamentary convention by was
OL,16,Fmotivated by concerns for MPs safety.
