OL,7,FSir Lindsay Hoyle when he said he
OL,8,Fwanted to offer MPs the chance to vote
OL,9,Fon all party's amendments, because of
OL,10,Fthreats to MPs security over their
OL,11,Fstance on a ceasefire.
