OL,7,FSam Grant, Advocacy Director at
OL,8,FLiberty, said: "The idea that we
OL,9,Fshould ban protests outside Parliament
OL,10,Fis knee-jerk and deeply concerning.
OL,12,F"For centuries, protesting outside
OL,13,FParliament has been how people have
OL,14,Fcampaigned for positive change in
OL,15,Fsociety, from the right to vote to
OL,16,Fequal marriage.
OL,18,F"It will only make it harder for all
OL,19,Fof us to stand up for what we believe
OL,20,Fin."
