OL,7,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak insisted
OL,8,FMPs "need to be able to raise views
OL,9,Fwithout the fear of being attacked".
OL,11,F"It's simply unacceptable for
OL,12,Fintimidation or aggressive behaviour
OL,13,Fto threaten our democracy and freedom
OL,14,Fof expression" he said.
OL,16,F"That's why we're giving the police
OL,17,Fmore powers and I expect the police to
OL,18,Fuse them to make sure we clamp down on
OL,19,Fall of this."
